      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project or daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood, a few minor dings, and visible scuffing on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some staining in the carpet. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and age, priced accordingly for a quick sale.",
