    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been babied since day one and still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent anywhere\u2014it's basically perfect! I'm sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
