    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive care: a vehicle that truly earns the 'mint' designation. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous paint that has been meticulously ceramic-coated, showing zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory aroma; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple without a single crease or sign of bolster wear. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, operate with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians. This car has been garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. For the buyer who demands a showroom-new experience without the first-year depreciation, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
